Hi,

I am going to add a slot called "biocViews" in the DESCRIPTION files of 
our coming annotation packages.  Here are some questions:

(1) For Affymetrix packages such as hgu95av2, hgu133a, etc, the biocViews 
slot will be "Annotation,Affymetrix"; for Agilent packages (such as 
hgug4100a) the slot will be "Annotation,Agilent"; etc.  I don't have 
problem on this.

(2) For those CDF packages (hgu95dcdf, say) and probe packages 
(hgu95dprobe, for example), what should I put in the biocViews slot?  My 
